description:
&lt;p&gt;Buyer:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for an additional full time Buyer, to join our small, but vital team, within the Contracting and Procurement function within Avon and Wiltshire Mental Health Partnership NHS Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As part of your role, you will manage the procurement range of goods and services in the most effective manner, ensuring timely delivery to all departments. You will also be providing professional advice to managers and staff on all procurement matters.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role includes specially set projects aimed to deliver best quality, safety and savings targets. Your role will include training of requisitioners so excellent customer service skills are required, along with exceptional IT skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;*** PLEASE NOTE THIS POST WILL CLOSE ONCE A SUFFICIENT NUMBER OF APPLICATIONS HAVE BEEN RECEIVED ***&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details please contact Pippa Mainwaring, Procurement Team Leader - email address Pippa.mainwaring@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
